"1/2 cup butter, melted","1/4 cup honey","2 tablespoons light brown sugar","1 teaspoon vanilla extract","1/8 teaspoon salt","3 cups uncooked regular oats","1 1/2 cups coarsely chopped pecans","1/2 cup toasted wheat germ","2 tablespoons sesame seeds","1  (8-oz.) package chopped dates"